text: Kevin O'Donnell may refer to: *Kevin O'Donnell (Peace Corps) (1925-2012), American who served as director of the Peace Corps *Kevin O'Donnell, Jr. (1950-2012), American science fiction writer, son of Peace Corps director *Kevin O'Donnell (footballer) (1924-2002), Australian rules footballer for St Kilda
title: Kevin O'Donnell
